@startuml
title UnoCash - Deployment and Control Flow Sequence Diagram

actor User
participant "Blazor WebAssembly\nSPA" as Blazor
participant "Azure API\nManagement" as APIM
participant "Azure Functions\nAPI" as Functions
participant "Azure Blob\nStorage" as BlobStorage
participant "Azure Table\nStorage" as TableStorage
participant "Azure Form\nRecognizer" as FormRecognizer
participant "Azure AD" as AD
participant "Pulumi\nIaC Engine" as Pulumi
participant "Azure\nResource Manager" as ARM

== Infrastructure Deployment Phase ==
Pulumi -> ARM: Provision Resource Group
activate ARM
ARM --> Pulumi: Resource Group Created
deactivate ARM

Pulumi -> ARM: Create Storage Account
activate ARM
ARM --> Pulumi: Storage Account Created
deactivate ARM

Pulumi -> ARM: Deploy Function App Service Plan
activate ARM
ARM --> Pulumi: Function App Created
deactivate ARM

Pulumi -> ARM: Configure API Management
activate ARM
ARM --> Pulumi: APIM Configured with Policies
deactivate ARM

Pulumi -> ARM: Setup Azure AD Application
activate ARM
ARM --> Pulumi: AD App Registered
deactivate ARM

Pulumi -> ARM: Configure DNS Records
activate ARM
ARM --> Pulumi: DNS Configured
deactivate ARM

== Application Runtime - Authentication Flow ==
User -> Blazor: Access Application
activate Blazor
Blazor -> AD: Request Authentication
activate AD
AD --> Blazor: Return Auth Token
deactivate AD
Blazor --> User: Display Home Page
deactivate Blazor

== Expense Creation Flow ==
User -> Blazor: Add New Expense
activate Blazor
Blazor -> APIM: POST /expenses (with Auth Token)
activate APIM
APIM -> APIM: Validate Auth & Apply Policies
APIM -> Functions: Forward AddExpense Request
activate Functions
Functions -> TableStorage: Write Expense Data
activate TableStorage
TableStorage --> Functions: Confirm Write
deactivate TableStorage
Functions --> APIM: Return Success
deactivate Functions
APIM --> Blazor: Response with Expense ID
deactivate APIM
Blazor --> User: Display Success
deactivate Blazor

== Receipt Upload and Processing Flow ==
User -> Blazor: Upload Receipt Image
activate Blazor
Blazor -> APIM: GET /receipt/upload-token
activate APIM
APIM -> Functions: GetReceiptUploadSasToken
activate Functions
Functions -> BlobStorage: Generate SAS Token
activate BlobStorage
BlobStorage --> Functions: Return SAS Token
deactivate BlobStorage
Functions --> APIM: Return Token
deactivate Functions
APIM --> Blazor: SAS Token Response
deactivate APIM

Blazor -> BlobStorage: Upload Receipt (using SAS Token)
activate BlobStorage
BlobStorage --> Blazor: Upload Complete
deactivate BlobStorage

Blazor -> APIM: POST /receipt/parse (Receipt URL)
activate APIM
APIM -> Functions: Trigger ReceiptParser
activate Functions
Functions -> TableStorage: Check Cache
activate TableStorage
TableStorage --> Functions: Cache Miss
deactivate TableStorage

Functions -> FormRecognizer: Analyze Receipt Image
activate FormRecognizer
FormRecognizer --> Functions: Extracted Data
deactivate FormRecognizer

Functions -> TableStorage: Store Parsed Result
activate TableStorage
TableStorage --> Functions: Confirm Storage
deactivate TableStorage

Functions --> APIM: Return Parsed Data
deactivate Functions
APIM --> Blazor: Receipt Data Response
deactivate APIM
Blazor --> User: Display Parsed Data
deactivate Blazor

== Expense Retrieval Flow ==
User -> Blazor: View Expenses
activate Blazor
Blazor -> APIM: GET /expenses
activate APIM
APIM -> APIM: Validate & Apply Policies
APIM -> Functions: GetExpenses Request
activate Functions
Functions -> TableStorage: Query Expenses
activate TableStorage
TableStorage --> Functions: Return Expense List
deactivate TableStorage
Functions --> APIM: Expense Data
deactivate Functions
APIM --> Blazor: Expense List Response
deactivate APIM
Blazor --> User: Display Expenses
deactivate Blazor

== Expense Update Flow ==
User -> Blazor: Update Expense
activate Blazor
Blazor -> APIM: PUT /expenses/{id}
activate APIM
APIM -> Functions: UpdateExpense Request
activate Functions
Functions -> TableStorage: Update Expense Record
activate TableStorage
TableStorage --> Functions: Confirm Update
deactivate TableStorage
Functions --> APIM: Success Response
deactivate Functions
APIM --> Blazor: Update Confirmed
deactivate APIM
Blazor --> User: Display Updated Data
deactivate Blazor

== Expense Deletion Flow ==
User -> Blazor: Delete Expense
activate Blazor
Blazor -> APIM: DELETE /expenses/{id}
activate APIM
APIM -> Functions: DeleteExpense Request
activate Functions
Functions -> TableStorage: Delete Expense Record
activate TableStorage
TableStorage --> Functions: Confirm Deletion
deactivate TableStorage
Functions --> APIM: Success Response
deactivate Functions
APIM --> Blazor: Deletion Confirmed
deactivate APIM
Blazor --> User: Update UI
deactivate Blazor

@enduml
